## Workflow

```bash
# 1. Create branch
git checkout main
git pull
git checkout -b feature/[name]

# 2. Work & commit
git add [files]
git commit -m "[type]: [message]"

# 3. Push
git push origin feature/[name]

# 4. Create PR via UI/CLI
```

