## Commit Format

```
[type]([scope]): [subject]

[optional body]

[optional footer]
```

**Types**: feat | fix | docs | style | refactor | test | chore

**Examples**:
- `feat(auth): add OAuth2 login`
- `fix(api): resolve timeout issue`
- `docs(readme): update setup instructions`

